This Package is called the Glade Code Generator(GCGEN)
Please Read The Copiying.txt before you install.

Requirements

1.Python >=2.5
2.PyXML >= 0.8.4

if you donot have the PyXML .. it is packaged with GcGen. just untar it and install it by saying 
--------------------------
"python setup.py install" 
--------------------------
Installation Directions
-----------------------------------
login as root (sudo su | su [i always recommend sudo]) and  
just say "python install.py"	   	
-----------------------------------
Running Instructions

Glade File must be in LigGlade Format

Run by typing
----------------------------------------------
gcgen [glade filename.glade] [codefilename.py]
----------------------------------------------

